snippet.title: Find the union of two sets
snippet.description:
http://www.freemathvideos.com In this playlist I show you how to understand set theory. I introduce sets as venn diagrams, mapping and as sets of numbers.  With sets we look at how to find the union, compliment, and intersection of given sets.  We introduce sets with two and three diagrams. http://www.freemathvideos.com presents: Learn math your way.  My mission is to provide quality math education to everyone that is willing to receive it. This video is only a portion of a video course I have created as a math teacher. Please visit my website to join my mailing list, download my new e-book, watch all of my free videos or register for one of my online courses. Thanks for watching and to your success.
